articles.author: Holly Ellyatt, Sophie Kiderlin, Karen Gilchrist
articles.title: European markets rise as traders assess changed U.S. political landscape, Ryanair tumbles 17.3% - CNBC
articles.description: European stocks closed higher Monday as global markets reacted to the news that U.S. President Joe Biden had dropped out of the U.S. presidential race.
